{"tid":490124,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"[科幻迷/穿越迷] 極力推薦Netflix新個套德國劇DARK","createTime":"2017-12-05T10:50:24.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-11T15:48:00.000Z","uid":22839,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"96511956bc9693fd9307156683881c236659f4f2","tid":490124,"uid":22839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-05T10:50:24.000Z","msg":"輕微劇透<br />\n<br />\n好多外媒搵呢套嘢直接同Stranger Things比較<br />\n因為故事設定都係小鎮<br />\n但我覺得無論世界觀同科幻設定都比Stranger Things仔細<br />\n懸疑感更強<br />\n套戲主題圍繞Time Travel，而其Time Travel理論係採用下圖最左邊個種，唔會有平衝宇宙，亦唔會因為改變咗過去而影響未來或現在。（主觀地認為呢種Time Travel Theory先係最有趣。）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/bc8Du.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fbc8Du.jpg&h=694d4522&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n當然套嘢都唔係無缺點<br />\n就係中段3-5集節奏較慢<br />\n而且角色唔算討好<br />\n<br />\nAnyway<br />\n2017年Netflix新劇嚟講<br />\n呢套必然係頭三"},{"pid":"b241c46deb69f6ec7c94ccc4ef3cba79e8c19ca5","tid":490124,"uid":56311,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-05T11:45:52.000Z","msg":"以為炒冷飯另一翻版ST<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48b2b7f28f04723cfb65030af211ec9cb2e0d268","tid":490124,"uid":41629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-05T16:09:25.000Z","msg":"遲下睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3986853227978f2398c886966735630d21a3be4b","tid":490124,"uid":65931,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T01:12:04.000Z","msg":"睇左第一集<br />\n悶到訓著左"},{"pid":"01f380db47599f207a5b0981cfb9159197fb62d8","tid":490124,"uid":21592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T15:48:00.000Z","msg":"係值得一睇, D 畫面都拍得好有氣氛"}]}